        <active>true</active>
        <article><![CDATA[<p>If you have the Tanium Performance module licensed and enabled in your environment, you may skip this step. If you do not, however, then set the <em>x_taniu_tan_core.performance_module_enabled</em> system property to <em>false</em>. This will alter the behavior of some features of Tanium Integration Core, and may even disable some features which are reliant on the Tanium Performance module. </p>]]></article>
